Start
/ `read photo.png, write to %photo%` builds with %photo% type=image kind=png. The action
/ Build resolves the extension to the high-level type (image); the type Build supplies
/ the kind (png). Runtime: file.read.Run() returns a Data tagged Type="image" carrying
/ an image.@this(bytes, mime="image/png").
- file.read photo.png, write to %photo%
- assert %photo% is not null
